igible human beings. This country must begin to make sacrifices and cut down the cost of governance.” Vanguard ABUJA- CHAIRMAN, Senate Committee on Culture and Tourism, Senator Rochas Okorocha, All Progressives Congress, APC, Imo North, yesterday raised the alarm that the cost of running the government and servicing the nation's budget was on the high side. October 3, 2019 In "News" Power truly corrupts, and like they say, absolute power corrupts absolutely. Governor Rochas Okorocha of Imo State is a reminder of the truism of this saying, because this appears to be his lot. November 10, 2018 In "Politics" Ordinarily, Saturday’s Senatorial Election in Imo West Senatorial District (Orlu Zone) would have been a walk over for Governor Rochas Okorocha who is contesting under the All Progressive Congress (APC). February 14, 2019 In "Viewpoint"